Package gw.api.activity

Class WorkplanFilterSet

java.lang.Object
gw.api.filters.FilterSetBase
gw.api.activity.ActivityFilterSetBase
gw.api.activity.WorkplanFilterSet
public class WorkplanFilterSet extends ActivityFilterSetBase
WorkplanFilterSet contains methods for computing filters of Activities based criteria such as whether the Activity is externally owned, open, assigned to the current user, and under assignemnet review.
